text: Good dental services. Pleasant waiting environment. Excellent dentist who takes good effort to answer all our queries & concerns. Good staffing too from the dental assistant to the receptionist. Highly recommended for aesthetic dental needs.

I was recommended to this clinic with an open mind. I love the friendly nurses and experienced doctors who treated my tooth . There is so much of ambient of CNY mood especially looking at how the clinic decorated  during this season . Both Dr.Tey and Dr.Tan are very friendly and kind people.  They are very knowledge in their skills.
I have been a regular patient of Dr Teh  at his clinic for more than 10 years, he is an extremely professional & friendly dentist.
Been treated by Dr tan for Invisalign. My whole family as well except father. Straight teeth highly recommended
I love the experience that i had in with all those friendly nurse and doctors ,they all serve customers with respect.
